                            <comment id="17441312" author="reta" created="Tue, 9 Nov 2021 18:15:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The message observer should be called in JAX-RS flows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Introduced new contextual property &lt;tt&gt;PROPAGATE_202_RESPONSE_ONEWAY_OR_PARTIAL&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;It is set to &lt;tt&gt;false&lt;/tt&gt; by default but JAX-RS clients override it with &lt;tt&gt;true&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
